org_self_serve.modals.true_up_edu.member.string: Members of your organization can upgrade people whenever they need to collaborate and co-edit. Newly added full seats are free until your true-up. Then, you’ll only be charged for the full seats you want to keep in your Organization going forward, and only for the prorated amount left on your annual contract.

org_self_serve.modals.true_up_edu.true_u.string: True-ups occur every three months starting from the date your organization was created. We’ll remind you several times leading up to your true-up, to review new paid seats added to your organization so you can decide whether or not to keep them. {seeFullDetails}
